{
  "stem": "23090.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's just like you would see in some of those [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] movies or stories, that these people, you know, when they gave-- when they said they were coming to visit these factories.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And these were all high-ranking officers with their wives, and it was an entourage of-- of-- of what I would call like the royalty.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we would all have to stand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they came in and examined the way we were working and how we were doing these things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the women were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was like a grand showing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was like a-- a wonderful, wonderful happening for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were-- they were examining the goods that were being made by us and shipped to them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So these inspections, I remember, would-- would be maybe two, three, or four times a year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They would come and examine how we worked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My dad-- no, my mother was not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- she was-- she was sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had a bad stomach, and so she couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my dad, of course, was a musician.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was also a policeman in the-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his duties was to, I guess, guard this and go there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure of exactly what his functions were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was part of the so-called government in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as a re-- thus as a result, we stayed longer and long-- We were the longest to stay there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because as I-- as people realized or not, doctors and policemen and government people stayed on so that they could [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] finish the-- the-- the evacuation of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they needed all these people to do so.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
